# Package Manager Preference: Use Bun

This project uses Bun as the preferred package manager and task runner.

-   Instead of `npm install`, use `bun install`.
-   Instead of `npm install <package>` or `npm i <package>`, use `bun add <package>`.
-   Instead of `npm uninstall <package>`, use `bun remove <package>`.
-   Instead of `npx <command>`, use `bunx <command>`.
